## 🌟 Features

- **🧑‍💻 Profile Creation**: Showcase your skills and experience
- **🤝 Team Matchmaking**: Find the perfect teammates for your next hackathon
- **🔔 Event Notifications**: Stay updated on the latest hackathon opportunities
- **💼 User Experience**: Seamless user experience with responsive design
